    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the mirror thing... it's exactly that. it feels like if i keep trying to hold the pieces together, i'm just hurting myself more. like, if a mirror is shattered, you don't keep trying to use it. you just accept that it's done. is it really worth the effort to keep trying to fix something that's clearly just meant to be in pieces?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
